{"tid":261194,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"現實中嘅IT狗就好似火箭兵團嘅果然翁一樣","createTime":"2017-05-28T09:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T12:12:14.000Z","uid":82050,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b94b1142567afa31ccf7b195eae50d5ef1c0874a","tid":261194,"uid":82050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"IT狗每日日常就係設法融入佢班朋友到,但係都係冇人理9鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n   就好似果然翁次次出黎 &quot;果然翁!!&quot; 都係冇人理鳩佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢嘅&quot;朋友&quot;一有事就需要IT狗幫手,而IT狗亦都樂於助人,但完事後係唔會得到任何嘅讚賞<br />\n<br />\n   就好似每次火箭兵團就打輸,頂唔緊,果然翁就會自己彈出黎同小次郎佢地食技,食完之後小次郎佢地就冇左件事,本身捉佢番黎就已經係想利用佢。<br />\n   有邊幾集啊,係會真心讚許果然翁啊?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當對IT狗無需要嘅時候,佢嘅朋友就會不約而同咁同IT狗講&quot;死撚開啦,阻撚住晒!&quot;<br />\n &quot;唔撚關你事啊!&quot; &quot;我搞得掂唔撚使你理!&quot; 根本就冇重視過佢<br />\n<br />\n   就好似有時果然翁自己行出黎果時候武藏就會塞番果然翁入精靈球,邊塞邊講&quot;死番入去啦,廢物!&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申: 9UP <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8695c8f9b1affb9ad7b9894afd9c589839eb0f4","tid":261194,"uid":47951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:11:38.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3a24a9c00366383b60978f8348aa17785bebddac","tid":261194,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:15:23.000Z","msg":"似毒氣丸多d"},{"pid":"a192dce5689c396e16cdd70c662502a45d1f0c80","tid":261194,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似毒氣丸多d</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人親近我"},{"pid":"51eb5fff0a72c01539bceb4093d28093a22b4736","tid":261194,"uid":82050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775131244a3462d93047323dfc3a02c1954cb166","tid":261194,"uid":26200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:26:42.000Z","msg":"果然翁係mk仔<img src=\"/as